{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a711548a02","title":"毛泽东转发华东军区关于打虎部署的报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"190c787541","index":0,"year":1952,"month":1,"day":27,"articleId":"a711548a02"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8da39f147a","type":"title","text":"毛泽东转发华东军区关于打虎部署的报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a711548a02"},{"id":"10ce33e7da","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a711548a02"},{"id":"4715bc1939","type":"appellation","text":"各大军区、志愿军，并告各中央局：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a711548a02"},{"id":"8f45ef1397","type":"paragraph","text":"华东军区的决心和部署均很好，请你们参酌办理。二月份全军发动打大老虎，至少应打二千只至三千只。二月份不整编，全力做三反。凡未检举坦白者，仍进行检查坦白，发现大批中小贪污，但中心应转入打老虎。这种任务的转变，有的可以在二月一日转，有的可以在二月五日或二月十日或二月十五日转，但至迟不得迟于二月十五日，由你们掌握。争取在二月二十八日全军老虎打完，结束三反。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a711548a02"},{"id":"4e23906cf7","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东一月二十七日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a711548a02"}],"page":{"id":"863cce5aad","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"a711548a02","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}